               <p>SECOND COUNT, for stealing like bank notes, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18130915-52-victim519" type="victimName">
                     John Pooley 
                     Kensington
                  <interp inst="t18130915-52-victim519" type="surname" value="Kensington"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130915-52-victim519" type="given" value="John Pooley"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130915-52-victim519" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , 
               
                  <persName id="t18130915-52-victim521" type="victimName">
                     Edward 
                     Kensington
                  <interp inst="t18130915-52-victim521" type="surname" value="Kensington"></interp>
